quran[128]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Ad ias lameô n Öebbi, ur pêirit $uôes. Gedha s yiS! Ay Aâlay, sennig wayen pcaraken."
  16,2,"Issrusu d lmalayek s ôôuê si lameô iS, $ef win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS: ""Nedôet ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, êezzbet iyI""."
  16,3,"Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Ay Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken!"
  16,4,"Ixelq ed amdan si tiqqit; atan iu$al aS, d axûim n ûûeê."
  16,5,"Ixelq awen d lmal, segsen iceîîiven iêman, aba$uô, u, segsen, teppeppem."
  16,6,"D ccbaêa nnwen mara ten id terrem, u mara ten teksem."
  16,7,"Ppawin tiâkkwmin nnwen ar tmurt ur teppawvem, siwa ma tâapbem. Ih, Mass nnwen, war ccekk, d Umâin, d Aênin."
  16,8,"Iâewdiwen, iserdyan, i$wyal, i rrekba nnwen akked ccbaêa. Ixelleq ayen ur tessinem."
  16,9,"D Öebbi i Ippawin d ubrid. Ff$en segs. Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Inhu meôôa."
  16,10,"D Neppa i wen d Isse$layen aman seg igenni. Segsen tissit nnwen, segsen ttjuô i itepp lmal."
  16,11,"Isskar awen d yissen nnaâma, azemmur, tizdayin, tiéuôin, akked yal ppemôa. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ipxemmimen."
  16,12,"Inub awen d s yiv akked wass, iîij akked waggur. Itran ppemnuben s lameô iS. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen."
  16,13,"I wen d Ixleq di tmurt, degs initen imgarraden. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ismektayen."
  16,14,"D Neppa i Inuben s yill, iwakken a pteppem, segs, aksum aleqqaq, a d teksem, segs, rrêuê i teppeqqnem. A pwaliv lbabuô ipcerrig it, iwakken a pnadim si lfevl iS, amar a ppesnemmrem."
  16,15,"Issers idurar $ef tmurt, ur teppembwiwil yiswen; isaffen, iberdan, amar a ppepwanham;"
  16,16,"timuliwin: s yitran, nitni pwanhan."
  16,17,"Day Win Ixelqen am win ur nxelleq? Day ur d tesmektayem ara?"
  16,18,"Lemmer a pêesbem l$it n Öebbi, ur tezmirem. Ih, Öebbi, war ccekk, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  16,19,"Öebbi Iéôa ayen teffrem akked wayen teqqaôem."
  16,20,"Wid u$uô pnujun, war Öebbi, ur illi wayen xelqen. D nitni i ipwaxelqen."
  16,21,"D lmeggtin ur d imuddiren, ur éôin melmi ara ten id ssekren."
  16,22,"Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen. Wid ur numin ara s laxeôt, d ulawen nnsen i iugin. U nitni pzzuxun."
  16,23,"War ccekk, Öebbi Iéôa ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaôen. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara imzuxiyen."
  16,24,"Ma nnan asen: ""d acu id Issers Mass nnwen""? Qqaôen: ""d timucuha imezwura""."
  16,25,"Ad bibben, ass n tnekra, tiâakkwmin nnsen, s pmam nnsent, akked wumur si tâakkwmin n wid telfen, mebla ma faqen. Day maççi dir it wayen bubben?"
  16,26,"Ih, undin p, wid i ten id izwaren. Öebbi Iaâtad lebni nnsen, si llsas. I$li d ssqef fellasen. Iusa ten id uâaqeb seg wanda ur bnin."
  16,27,"Sinna, ass n tnekra, a ten Idull, ad Yini: ""anda ten icriken iW, i$ef temnamarem""? Nnan imawlan n tussna: ""war ccekk, ddell akked ddens, assa, $ef ijehliyen"
  16,28,"iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, nitni densen iman nnsen"". A d ssutren tifrat: ""ur nexdim kra n tucmip"". Xaîi, Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa ayen txeddmem."
  16,29,"Kecmet si tebbura, ar Loahennama; degs a pwekkôem. A yicmet uxxam imzuxiyen!"
  16,30,"Ad inin i wid ipêezziben: ""d acu id Issers Mass nnwen""? A d inin: ""d lxiô"". I wid imaânen, ise$ di ddunit agi. Pifxiô, war ccekk, axxam aneggaru. Ay d umâin uxxam n wid ipêezziben!"
  16,31,"Ad kecmen leonanat n Âaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen; degsen, i nitni, ayen i sen ihwan. Akka i Ipkafi Öebbi wid ipêezziben,"
  16,32,"wid iwumi ddment lmalayek leôwaê, nitni maânen, ad asen inint: ""tifrat fellawen! Kecmet Loennet, ilmend n wayen txeddmem""."
  16,33,"Day a pôaoun kan tisin n lmalayek $uôsen, ne$ a d iawev lameô n Mass ik? Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi, maca densen iman nnsen."
  16,34,"D tucmitin xeddmen, i ten iwwten. Izzi yasen wayen i$ef pmmaâliken."
  16,35,"Nnan wid ipcaraken: ""Lemmer i S ihwi i Öebbi, ur naâbed acemma, war Neppa, nekwni akked imezwura nne$. Ur negdel acemma, war ayen Igdel"". Akka ay xedmen imezwura nnsen. Day illa wayen iwatan i Umazan, siwa awal ipbegginen?"
  16,36,"Ni$ Nuzen ed amazan i yal lois: ""âabdet Öebbi, janbet iôebbiten n tkerkas"". Garasen, llan wid Inha Öebbi; garasen, wid i$ef iura ttelfan. Iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d inekkaôen."
  16,37,"Xas tôe$wbev $ef nnhaya nnsen, Öebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu wid Itlef. Ur asen illi usettaô."
  16,38,"Ggulen s Öebbi, liman iûeêêan nnsen, ar ur d Ippara ara Öebbi wid immuten. Xaîi, lemâahda fellas d tidep, maca tegwti n medden ur ssinen."
  16,39,"Iwakken ad asen d ibeggen ayen i$ef mgarraden, iwakken ad éôen wid ijehlen, ar nitni, war ccekk, llan d ikeddaben."
  16,40,"Awal nne£ kan, i t$awsa, ma Neb$a p, ad as Nini: ""ili""! A ppili."
  16,41,"Wid iunagen i Öebbi, mbaâd ma pwadensen, a ten Nesserked di ddunit s yise$. Arraz n laxeôt a t i$leb, war ccekk, lemmer éôin"
  16,42,"wid iûebôen u ppeklen $ef Mass nnsen."
  16,43,"Id Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen iwumi Nweêêa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teéôim ara."
  16,44,"S ubeggen akked Ihellilen, Nuzen ak d asmekti, iwakken a pbeggnev i medden, ayen i sen d irsen, amar a d mmektin."
  16,45,"Wid iundin tucmitin, aâni $ilen ur Iôemmu ara Öebbi di tmurt, ne$ ur ten id ippawev ara uâaqeb, seg wanda ur bnin?"
  16,46,"Ne$ ur ten id ikkat ara di cce$l nnsen, ur sfunnugen?"
  16,47,"Ne$ ur ten ikkat ara cwiî, cwiî. Ih, Mass nnwen, war ccekk, Issuruf, Ipêunu."
  16,48,"Day ur walan ara ayen akw Ixleq Öebbi, ippara tili s yeffus, zelmev; tkennu i Öebbi, s wannuz."
  16,49,"I Öebbi ikennu meôôa wayen illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt, imexlaq akked lmalayek. Nitni ur sme$wôen iman nnsen."
  16,50,"Ppagwaden Mass nnsen, sennig sen, xeddmen ayen i sen ippumôen."
  16,51,"Inna Öebbi: ""ur sâut sin iôebbiten. Neppa, d Öebbi Yiwen kan. Ihi, Nek, agwadet iyI""."
  16,52,"IneS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Ddin, ineS i lebda. Day a têezzbem i war Öebbi?"
  16,53,"S$uô Öebbi, ayen akw ikwen i$aten. D$a mi kwen têuza lemveôôa, $uôeS ay tnedhem."
  16,54,"Sinna, mi wen Ikkes lemveôôa, arbaâ segwen, atnan pcaraken i Mass nnsen."
  16,55,"Nekôen, akka, i sen Nefka. Zhut, deqqal a ppeéôem."
  16,56,"La qesden, i wur ssinen, amur seg wayen is iten Neôzeq. S Öebbi, ar fellawen asteqsi, $ef wayen id tesnulfuyem!"
  16,57,"Gern aS d, i Öebbi, tullas. Gedha s yiS! I nitni, ayen ssarmen."
  16,58,"Ma becceôn yiwen s teqcict, ad yibrik wudem is, ad iqbeô."
  16,59,"Ad iveôôef iman is, si medden, ilmend n yir usali it id ibbwven. A p ijmaâ, tamara, ne$ a p irr seddaw wakal? Ay dir wamek debbiôen!"
  16,60,"I wid ur numin ara s laxert: amedya ucmit. I Öebbi: amedya aâlayen mavi. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab."
  16,61,"Öebbi, lemmer Ipqissi medden, $ef ddens nnsen, ur d Ippaoa, degs, amexluq. Maca, Iswexxiô iten ar lajel ipwassnen. Ma iusa d lajel nnsen, ur t swexxiôen, ur t id seqôaben, s ssaâa."
  16,62,"Garen aS d, i Öebbi, ayen keôhen. Skaddben yilsawen nnsen, mi qqaôen ar ayen ilhan, nnsen. Ay nnsen, war ccekk, d times. Ih, nitni ad zwiren."
  16,63,"S Öebbi, ni$ Nuzen ed, i leoyus, uqbel ik. Cciîan icebbeê asen igiten nnsen. Assa, d bab nnsen. I nitni, aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  16,64,"Nessader ak edTazmamt, iwakken kan ad asen tbeggnev ayen i$ef mgarraden, akw i nnhaya akked uêunu i ugdud iumnen."
  16,65,"Öebbi Isse$li d aman, seg igenni. Issader yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud isellen."
  16,66,"Ih, ameyyez, i kunwi, di lmal. Nesswa kwen s wayen illan deg ufwad nnsen, ger lfert d idamen, i$i iûfan, aéidan i wid itessen."
  16,67,"Si ppemôa n tezdayin akked tfeôôant, teppawim d ayen iûûekôen, akked ôôezq igerzen. Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ifehmen."
  16,68,"Iweêêa Mass ik i tzizwa: ""gemt ixxamen deg durar, di ttjuô, di te$wôasin."
  16,69,"Sinna, eççemt si yal ppemôa. Ddumt s wannuz, iberdan n Mass nnkwent. Iteffe$ ed seg iâabbav nnsent ayen tessen, n yal ini, degs êellu i imdanen"". Deg waya, s tidep, assekni i ugdud ipxemmimen."
  16,70,"Ixelq ikwen Öebbi, sinna, ad awen Iddem ôôuê. Kra, segwen, ad ccerfeffen mavi, alamma ur ppissinen acemma mbaâd ma ssnen. Ih, Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Aêernuk."
  16,71,"Öebbi Ismenyaf ad I$it kra i wiyav. Wid Ismenyaf, ur ilaq ara ad rren, ôôeéq nnsen, i waklan nnsen, d$a ad âadlen yidsen. Day ara nekôen l$it n Öebbi?"
  16,72,"Iga yawen Öebbi, seg iman nnwen, tilawin nnwen. Ifka yawen, si tlawin nnwen, arraw d warraw n warraw. Iôeéq ikwen s wayen ilhan. Day ad amnen di tkerkas, ad nekôen l$it n Öebbi?"
  16,73,"Âabden, war Öebbi, wid ur nesâi acemma, swayes ara ten ôeéqen, si tmurt akked igenwan, u ur zmiren."
  16,74,"Ur d ppawit imedyaten i Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem."
  16,75,"Ifka d Öebbi amedya n wakli, d ayla, ur izmir i wacemma, akked yiwen iwumi Nefka, s $uône£, ôôeéq ilhan. Ipseddiq, segs, s tuffra ne$ âinani. Day âadlen? Ccekôan i Öebbi. Maca, tegwti, segsen, ur ssinen."
  16,76,"Ifka d Öebbi amedya n sin irgazen. Yiwen d agugam, ur izmir i wacemma. D taâkkwemt i bab is. Anda it iuzen, ur d ippawi lxiô. Day iaâdel akked win ippamôen lêeqq, u neppa deg ubrid uwqim?"
  16,77,"N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Lameô n yimir, am unqaj n tiî kan, ne$ ur ibbwiv. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci."
  16,78,"Öebbi Issuffe$ ikwen id si tâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen, ur tessinem acemma. Ifka yawen timejjin, iéôi, ul, amar a ppesnemmrem."
  16,79,"Day ur walan ara ifôax, têeppem fellasen lhawa igenni, ur ten iîîif yiwen siwa Öebbi? Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen."
  16,80,"Öebbi Irra yawen ixxamen nnwen d tanezdu$t. Irra yawen ixxamen, s igwelman n lmal nnwen. Fessusit, ass n yinig, d wass uqeggel. Taduî nnsen, ccâaô nnsen, inéaden nnsen, i leêwal akked dduzan, tallit kan."
  16,81,"Deg wayen Ixleq, Öebbi Ifka yawen d tili. Irra yawen, deg idurar, ûûôanat. Ifka yawen iceîîiven i kwen isdarayen seg u$amac, iceîîiven i kwen ipfukkun si lbe$wv nnwen. Akka, ad awen Itim l$it iS. Amar a ppanzem."
  16,82,"Ma wexxôen, i illan fellak, siwa awal ipbegginen."
  16,83,"Âaqlen l$it n Öebbi, sinna, nekôen t. Tegwti, degsen, d ijehliyen."
  16,84,"Ass ideg ara d Nessker, si yal lois, anagi, imiren ur ippili tesriê i wid ijehlen, u nitni ur ste$fiôen"
  16,85,"Mi walan, imednas, aâaqeb, ur ippifsus fellasen, ur ppestaâfun."
  16,86,"Mi walan, wid ipcaraken, wid curken, ad inin: ""a Mass nne$! D wigi i d icriken nne$ u$uô nepnuju, war Keçç"". Ad asen d rren: ""kunwi, war ccekk, d ikeddaben""."
  16,87,"Assen, ad fken mayna i Öebbi. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen."
  16,88,"Wid ijehlen, u sîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, Nerna yasen aâaqeb sennig wayev, ilmend n wayen ssefsaden."
  16,89,"Ass ideg ara d Nessker, i yal lois, anagi segsen, fellasen, a k id Nawi d anagi mgal wigi. Nessers ak d Tazmamt, d abeggen n yal cci, d nnhaya, d aêunu, u d abecceô i imvuâen."
  16,90,"Ih, Öebbi Iumeô ed lêeqq, akked lewqama, talalt i llzem. Igdel tucmitin, ayen n dir, ddeôk. A kwen Ipnabi, amar a d temmektim."
  16,91,"Eîîfet di lemâahda n Öebbi ma tâahdem. Ur êentet di tgallit ma tetebbtem, u tcubkem Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa acu txeddmem."
  16,92,"Ur cebbut tin ifsin lxiv is, mbaâd ma tcudd it, s loehd. Tepparam tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen: ad ikk lois sennig wayev. Öebbi Ipjeôôib ikwen kan, yis. War ccekk, ad awen Ibeggen, ass n tnekra, ayen i$ef temgarradem."
  16,93,"Lemmer i S ihwi, i Öebbi, a kwen Irr d yiwen n lois. Maca, Itellif win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. S tidep, a ppepusteqsim $ef wayen txeddmem."
  16,94,"Ur pparat tagallit nnwen i umkellex garawen. Ad iccev uvaô mbaâd ma iîîef. A pjeôbem tawa$it, ilmend n wayen tveôôfem seg ubrid n Öebbi. I kunwi, aâaqeb abarar."
  16,95,"Ur ppa$et s lemâahda n Öebbi ayen ôxisen. Ih, yif it i kunwi wayen illan $eô Öebbi, lemmer teéôim."
  16,96,"Ayen illan $uôwen, ad ifukk; ayen illan $eô Öebbi, ad idum. War ccekk, a Nkafi wid iûebôen, s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen."
  16,97,"Wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta, u umnen, a ten Nessider di tmeddurt tumâint, a ten Nkafi s wazal n wayen xeddmen ifuqen."
  16,98,"Mara te$ôev Leqwôan, ssuter a k Iaâteq Öebbi, si Cciîan imenfi."
  16,99,"Neppa, s tidep, ur isâi adabu $ef wid iumnen, i ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen."
  16,100,"Adabu ines, $ef wid kan i t irran d bab, d wid i S ipcaraken."
  16,101,"Ma Nbeddel assekni s ussekni, u Öebbi Yif akw akken Issen ayen id Issers, a d inin: ""keçç, d win kan id isnulfuyen"". Xaîi! Tegwti, degsen, ur ssinen."
  16,102,"Ini: ""Issers it id ôôuê iôqan, s$uô Mass ik, s tidep, iwakken ad itebbet wid iumnen; d nnhaya u d abecceô i imvuâen""."
  16,103,"Ih, Neéôa, qqaôen: ""d amdan kan it isselmaden"". Tameslayt n win d gren, d tabeôôanit, wagi d awal aâôab n ûûeê."
  16,104,"Ih, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi, ur ten Inehhu Öebbi. I nitni, aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  16,105,"Ih, gren d kan tikerkas, wid ur numin ara s issekniyen n Öebbi. Widak, d nitni ay d ikeddaben."
  16,106,"Win inekôen Öebbi, deffir liman is, siwa ma êeppmen fellas, u ul is izga iumen…. Ma d wid illin idmaren nnsen, ar tijehli, ad Izâaf Öebbi fellasen. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar."
  16,107,"Ayagi, acku smenyafen tameddurt n ddunit i laxeôt. Ih, Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud ijehliyen."
  16,108,"D wigi iwumi Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, timejjin nnsen, iéôi nnsen. Wigi d i$efliyen."
  16,109,"War ccekk, nitni, di laxeôt, ad ilin d imexsuôen."
  16,110,"Sinna, Mass ik, s tidep, i wid iunagen mbaâd ma thewwlen, sinna juhden, ûebôen; ih, Mass ik, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  16,111,"Ass ideg ara d ias, yal yiwen, ad inamer $ef yiman is, u yal yiwen ad iîîukafi $ef wayen ixdem, nitni ur pwadensen."
  16,112,"Ifka d Öebbi amedya n temdint, i illan di laman u îîmana. Ippas ip id ôôeéq is, s lufa, si yal tama. Tenkeô l$it n Öebbi. Isukk Öebbi fellas tawa$it n llaé akked lweêc, ilmend n wayen la ûûenâan."
  16,113,"Ni$ iusa ten id umazan, segsen. Skaddben t, iwwet iten uâaqeb, nitni densen."
  16,114,"Eççet seg wayen is ikwen I$at Öebbi, i iêellen, i imaânen. Snemmret l$it n Öebbi, ma d Neppa ay tâabdem."
  16,115,"I yawen Igdel siwa loifa, idim, aksum n yilef, akked wayen id irsen s yisem ur nelli d win n Öebbi. Ma d win terra tmara, ur ijuô, ur inufeq, Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  16,116,"Ur qqaôet tikerkas id ppawin ilsawen nnwen: ""aya d leêlal, aya d leêôam"". A d tegrem tikerkas $ef Öebbi. Wid id iggaren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, ur rebêen."
  16,117,"Drus ara zhun, fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  16,118,"I wudayen, Negdel ayen i$ef i k Neêka, iu$ lêal. Ur ten Nednis, maca nitni ddennisen iman nnsen."
  16,119,"Sinna, Mass ik, i wid ixedmen cceôô, ur ssinen, d$a steôoâen deffir waya, u sweqmen, Mass ik, war ccekk, deffir waya, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  16,120,"Ibôahim, ih, d amdan i imalen ar tidep, i iunzen i Öebbi. Ur illi seg imcurak."
  16,121,"Isnemmar l$it iS. Ifren it u Inha t s abrid uwqim."
  16,122,"Nefka yas di ddunit ise$, u, di laxeôt, neppa, s tidep, ad yili seg izedganen."
  16,123,"Sinna, Nweêêa yak d a ppedduv d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak."
  16,124,"Ssebt, iu$al kan i wid imgarraden fellas. Ih, Mass ik ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen llan mgarraden."
  16,125,"Enced s abrid n Mass ik, s ûûwab akked nnhaya tumâint. Mmeslay iten, s yiles aéidan mavi. Ih, Mass ik Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i iff$en seg ubrid iS. Neppa Yif akw akken Issen, anwi i ipwanhan."
  16,126,"Ma tâaqbem, âaqbet akken teppuâaqbem. Ma tûebôem, yif it i iûebôiyen."
  16,127,"Eûbeô. Üûebô ik s Öebbi kan. Ur $webben ilmend nnsen, ur pveyyiq si tcengal nnsen."
  16,128,"Ih, Öebbi Atan ar wid ipêezziben, akked wid issewqamen."
